    h2 Getting Started
    p Luxa CSS is simple and focused; its goal is to provide a lightweight solution easily implemented in any development context.
    p
        | With simple class names like&nbsp;
        span.code .lx-btn
        | &nbsp;or&nbsp;
        span.code .lx-row
        | , and a simple modifier system, like&nbsp;
        span.code .is-left
        | , it is easy to learn and use.
