    h3 Customize, Rewrite or Change
    p Want to customize, rewrite or change something, to suit your needs better?
    p Start by cloning the repository:
    .code-box
        .code
            span.line git clone https://github.com/luxonauta/luxa.git
    p
        | This project needs&nbsp;
        a(
            href="https://nodejs.org/en/",
            target="_blank",
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
        ) Node
        | , as the project uses&nbsp;
        a(
            href="https://gulpjs.com/",
            target="_blank",
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
        ) Gulp
        | .
    p Make sure it is installed, with the following commands:
    .code-box
        .code
            span.line node --version
            br
            span.line npm --version
            br
            span.line npx --version
    p
        | If not, follow the&nbsp;
        a(
            href="https://nodejs.org/en/",
            target="_blank",
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
        ) instructions here
        | .
    p After, install the Gulp command line utility;
    p
        | Install it following the&nbsp;
        a(
            href="https://gulpjs.com/docs/en/getting-started/quick-start/",
            target="_blank",
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
        )
            i.fas.fa-link
            | Gulp installation tutorial
        | , or run the command on the terminal:
    .code-box
        .code
            span.line npm i
    p
        b Verify your Gulp versions
    .code-box
        .code
            span.line gulp --version
    p
        b Then test it!
    p Now all you have to do is initialize it:
    .code-box
        .code
            span.line npm run gulp
    p And you're ready!
